`8Keywords``   : Critical_Strike
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

Critical Strike is an ability to hit vital areas of the body and thus inflict
more damage per hit.  This is a result of a Knight's rigorous training in
martial ways and therefore is an innate ability only for them.

